<p><strong>Analysis</strong>: Platform bill matches invoice, indicating accurate platform billing. But recharge exceeds spend by $520—this could be unspent balance or recharge fees. Need to further confirm whether current account balance matches.</p>
<hr />
<h2>Closing Thoughts</h2>
<p>Overseas ad reconciliation is ultimately an 'information synchronization' problem. Recharge, spend, and invoice naturally scatter across different systems and platforms. Only by actively aligning them can you truly grasp your account's financial health.</p>
<p>In serving our clients, 以渔 has found that <strong>teams with clear financials make scaling decisions faster, maintain steadier recharge rhythms, and breeze through investor due diligence</strong>. If your team is still reconciling via screenshots and memory, start today by establishing a basic reconciliation template—no complex systems needed. Just writing the three data sources into one sheet is the first step.</p>
